# M3V3

[Go back](https://github.com/seanpm2001/SNU/wiki/)

M3V3 (Milestone 3 version 3) is the third milestone build of SNU 3.0. It contains minor improvements. It is in its very basic form, and uses some of Seans very old HTML methods.

## Info

Version number: `3.0.2`

Development start date: `February 1st 2019`

Development end date: `February 8th 2019`

License: `GNU General Public License 3.0`

Languages: `English`

Computer languages: `HTML 5.3, Python 3.7, ActionScript 2.0/3.0, Ada, C, Haskell, Java, Lua, Pascal, Perl, PHP, Ruby, Rust`

Version size: `Not available`

Preceeded by: [SNU 3.0.1 (M3V2)](https://github.com/seanpm2001/SNU/Wiki/M3V2)

Succeeded by: [SNU 3.0.3 (M3V4)](https://github.com/seanpm2001/SNU/Wiki/M3V4)
